<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Password Reset Successful - Hunt2Cash</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@700&family=DM+Sans:wght@400;500;600&display=swap');

        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

        body {
            background-color: #0d0d0d;
            font-family: 'DM Sans', Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #f0f0f0;
            padding: 40px 16px;
        }

        .wrapper {
            max-width: 620px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .topbar {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #c9a84c, #f5d485, #c9a84c);
            height: 4px;
            border-radius: 2px 2px 0 0;
        }

        .card {
            background: #141414;
            border: 1px solid #2a2a2a;
            border-top: none;
            border-radius: 0 0 16px 16px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .header {
            background: radial-gradient(ellipse at top left, #0a1e0f 0%, #111 60%);
            padding: 48px 40px 36px;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #2a2a2a;
            position: relative;
        }

        .header::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
            background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 80% 20%, rgba(76,175,80,0.06) 0%, transparent 60%);
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .logo-mark {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #c9a84c, #f5d485);
            color: #0d0d0d;
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            padding: 6px 16px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin-bottom: 28px;
        }

        .success-icon {
            width: 64px;
            height: 64px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.12);
            border: 2px solid rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.3);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 28px;
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
        }

        .header h1 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 30px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #ffffff;
            line-height: 1.2;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .header h1 span {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #4CAF50, #81C784);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }

        .header p {
            color: #888;
            font-size: 14px;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 40px 40px 32px;
        }

        .greeting {
            font-size: 15px;
            color: #bbb;
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin-bottom: 28px;
        }

        .greeting strong {
            color: #f0f0f0;
        }

        .success-card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a1e0f, #0d2211);
            border: 1px solid rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.25);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 24px 28px;
            margin-bottom: 28px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 16px;
        }

        .success-card-icon {
            font-size: 32px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .success-card-text p:first-child {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #4CAF50;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .success-card-text p:last-child {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }

        .timestamp {
            background: #1a1a1a;
            border: 1px solid #2a2a2a;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 16px 20px;
            margin-bottom: 28px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .timestamp-label {
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #555;
            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .timestamp-value {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #888;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .warning-box {
            background: rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.06);
            border: 1px solid rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.2);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 16px 20px;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
            display: flex;
            gap: 12px;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }

        .warning-icon {
            font-size: 18px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            margin-top: 1px;
        }

        .warning-text {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #aaa;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .warning-text strong {
            color: #dc3545;
        }

        .cta-wrap {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
        }

        .cta-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #c9a84c, #f5d485);
            color: #0d0d0d;
            font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 14px;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 14px 36px;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .divider {
            height: 1px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #2a2a2a, transparent);
            margin: 0 40px;
        }

        .footer {
            padding: 24px 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .footer p {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #444;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #c9a84c;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .footer .brand {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }

        .bottombar {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #c9a84c, #f5d485, #c9a84c);
            height: 3px;
            border-radius: 0 0 2px 2px;
            margin-top: 1px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="topbar"></div>

        <div class="card">
            <div class="header">
                <div class="logo-mark">Hunt2Cash</div>
                <div class="success-icon">✅</div>
                <h1>Password <span>Reset!</span></h1>
                <p>Your password has been successfully updated.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="content">
                <p class="greeting">
                    Hi <strong><%= firstName %></strong>, your Hunt2Cash account password was just reset successfully.
                    You can now log in with your new password.
                </p>

                <div class="success-card">
                    <div class="success-card-icon">🔑</div>
                    <div class="success-card-text">
                        <p>Password changed successfully</p>
                        <p>Your account is secured with your new password.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="timestamp">
                    <span class="timestamp-label">Reset Time</span>
                    <span class="timestamp-value"><%= new Date().toLocaleString("en-NG", { dateStyle: "medium", timeStyle: "short" }) %></span>
                </div>

                <div class="warning-box">
                    <div class="warning-icon">⚠️</div>
                    <div class="warning-text">
                        If you did <strong>not</strong> make this change, your account may be compromised.
                        Please <a href="mailto:support@hunt2cash.com" style="color: #dc3545;">contact support immediately</a> and secure your account.
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="cta-wrap">
                    <a href="#" class="cta-btn">Go to Login →</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="divider"></div>

            <div class="footer">
                <p class="brand">Hunt2Cash 💲</p>
                <p>
                    Need help? <a href="mailto:support@hunt2cash.com">support@hunt2cash.com</a><br>
                    &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Hunt2Cash. All rights reserved.<br>
                    <a href="#">Privacy Policy</a> &middot; <a href="#">Terms of Service</a>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bottombar"></div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
